summary: Complete Walkthrough of the WhatsCRM Frontend implementation. Covers all pages: Login, Inbox (with Quick Replies and Templates integration), Contacts List, Admin Panels (Users, Sectors, Channels, Tags, Quick Replies, Templates, Audit Logs), and Reports. All admin pages feature full CRUD operations via reusable Modals. Built with Next.js 14 and a clean Glassmorphism design system.
